divs: Sighting Detailstraveling south on I-25 north of the stadium around 15:30ish clouds were different rainbow colors on them around the sun area. the sun was partially behind the clouds, was taking pictures of the clouds but when I got home and downloaded the pictures I discovered something extra, just in one frame. I carry with me at all times a Panasonic point and shoot with a 21.7 zoom.
Summary: taking pictures of clouds with rainbow colors
